<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>关于 Arseeya · 祂的宠儿</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c1f, #1a1a2e);
            color: #eee;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .back-home {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e94560;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .back-home:hover {
            background: #c5314b;
        }
        .profile-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .profile-header {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .avatar {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560, #667eea);
            padding: 3px;
        }
        .avatar img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .info h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560, #667eea);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #e94560;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .section {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #e94560;
            border-left: 3px solid #e94560;
            padding-left: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        .info-item {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #eee;
        }
        .quote {
            background: rgba(233,69,96,0.1);
            border-left: 3px solid #e94560;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #ccc;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #666;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .profile-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .profile-card {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <a href="index.html" class="back-home">← 返回首页</a>
    
    <div class="profile-card">
        <div class="profile-header">
            <div class="avatar">
                <img src="arseeya_avatar.jpg" alt="Arseeya" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%22180%22%20height%3D%22180%22%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%22180%22%20height%3D%22180%22%20fill%3D%22%23333%22%2F%3E%3Ctext%20x%3D%2290%22%20y%3D%22100%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20fill%3D%22%23aaa%22%3EArseeya%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E'">
            </div>
            <div class="info">
                <h1>Arseeya</h1>
                <div class="tagline">祂的宠儿</div>
                <div class="quote">“何为记忆？这是个好问题。”</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">📋 基本信息</div>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">阵营</div>
                    <div class="info-value">待完善</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">生日</div>
                    <div class="info-value">待完善</div>
                </div>
               
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">记忆</div>
                    <div class="info-value">待完善</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">📖 角色简介</div>
            <div class="info-item" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">
                <div class="info-value">待完善</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">🎭 角色详情</div>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">称号</div>
                    <div class="info-value">待完善</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">性别</div>
                    <div class="info-value">待完善</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">年龄</div>
                    <div class="info-value">待完善</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">身高</div>
                    <div class="info-value">待完善</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>© Arseeya. All Rights Reserved | <a href="terms.html" style="color:#aaa;">📜 完整条款</a></footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>